  &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400 !important; font-size: 1.3em !important; color: #000;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/180515/rss" title="spin.atomicobject.com" style=" color: #D94306;"&gt;A Guide to Browser DevTools - The Network Monitor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; ‚Äî Provides a solid starting point for getting to grips with the Network Monitor in your workflow ‚Äî a tool that allows us to see and inspect the requests a browser makes as a page¬†loads.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Michael Li &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
